videos.description: Tulane running back Cameron Carroll goes through the defense and into the end zone for Tulane's first score of the day.

videos.headline: Carroll gets Tulane on the board with a short TD

videos.description: Tulane runs the jet sweep as Phat Watts finds the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Tulane runs jet sweep for 2nd TD of the day

videos.description: Cameron Carroll weaves his way through the defense and finds the end zone for the 24-yard touchdown.

videos.description: Navy earns a first down after wide receiver Myles Fells throws the pass to quarterback Dalen Morris.

videos.headline: Navy gets the first down off the trick play

videos.description: Mark Walker hauls in the 44-yard pass, getting Navy to the 1-yard line. On the next play, Nelson Smith scores the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Walker's long reception leads to Smith's TD for Navy) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Walker's long reception leads to Smith's TD for Navy

videos.description: Jamale Carothers bursts up the middle for 48 yards, and a few plays later Nelson Smith scores his second touchdown of the day to bring Navy within 10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carothers’ long run sets up Smith’s 2nd Navy TD of the day) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carothers' long run sets up Smith's 2nd Navy TD of the day

videos.description: After trailing 24-0 earlier in the game, Navy scores forces a safety late in the third quarter to make the score 24-16.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Navy continues their comeback with a safety) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Navy continues their comeback with a safety

videos.description: Dalen Morris throws a dime to Mychal Cooper for the TD, and Navy then converts their two-point attempt, bringing them all the way back from 24-0 deficit.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cooper ties it for Navy with a long TD reception) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cooper ties it for Navy with a long TD reception

videos.description: Daniel Davies puts through the field goal, giving Navy a 27-24 win after trailing 24-0 at halftime.
